-26" id="cite_note-26"><a href="./Ethnic_group#cite_ref-26" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-26" class="mw-reference-text">Banton, Michael. (2007) "Weber on Ethnic Communities: A critique", <i id="mwAg0">Nations and Nationalism 13</i> (1), 2007, 19–35.</span></li><li about="#cite_note-cohen-27" id="cite_note-cohen-27"><span rel="mw:referencedBy"><a href="./Ethnic_group#cite_ref-cohen_27-0"><span class="mw-linkback-text">1 </span></a><a href="./Ethnic_group#cite_ref-cohen_27-1"><span class="mw-linkback-text">2 </span></a><a href="./Ethnic_group#cite_ref-cohen_27-2"><span class="mw-linkback-text">3 </span></a><a href="./Ethnic_group#cite_ref-cohen_27-3"><span class="mw-linkback-text">4 </span></a><a href="./Ethnic_group#cite_ref-cohen_27-4"><span class="mw-linkback-text">5 </span></a></span> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-cohen-27" class="mw-reference-text">Ronald Cohen 1978 "Ethnicity: Problem and Focus in Anthropology", <i id="mwAg4">Annual Review of Anthropology</i> 7: 383-384 Palo Alto: Stanford University Press</span></li><li about="#cite_note-28" id="cite_note-28"><a href="./Ethnic_group#cite_ref-28" rel="mw:referencedBy"><span class="mw-linkback-text">↑ </span></a> <span id="mw-reference-text-cite_note-28" class="mw-reference-text"><cite class="citation journal" about="#mwt97" typeof="mw:Transclusion" data-mw='{"parts":[{"template":{"target":{"wt":"Cite journal ","href":"./Template:Cite_journal"},"params":{"year":{"wt":"2015"},"last1":{"wt":"James"},"first1":{"wt":"Paul"},"authorlink1":{"wt":"Paul James (academic)"},"title":{"wt":"Despite the Terrors of Typologies: The Importance of Understanding Categories of Difference and Identity"},"url":{"wt":"https://www.academia.edu/11768378/_Despite_the_Terrors_of_Typologies_The_Importance_of_Understanding_Categories_of_Difference_and_Identity_"},"journal":{"wt":"Interventions: International Journal of Postcolonial Studies"},"volume":{"wt":"1